Of note:

&quot;Laid down, 23 May 1941 by the Luders Marine Construction Co., Stamford, CT; Launched, 27 April 1942; Commissioned USS SC-534, 11 July 1942; Decommissioned, (date unknown); Transferred to France, 28 October 1944; Redesignated CH-122; Struck from the Naval Register, (date unknown); Fate unknown.&quot;

